cs.LG, cs.AI, cs.DB, cs.SI, cs.CL 

The paper discusses machine learning models for dynamic graphs, which is a topic that falls under the sub-categories of machine learning (cs.LG), artificial intelligence (cs.AI), databases (cs.DB), social and information networks (cs.SI), and computational linguistics (cs.CL). However, since the focus is on representation learning, which is a core topic in machine learning, cs.LG is the most likely sub-category. The other sub-categories are also relevant because they involve applications and techniques that are discussed in the paper.
